data.title: Drake – 8am in Charlotte
data.meta_description: 8am in Charlotte Lyrics: In God's hands (Conductor) / Be grateful / That He was there / Glory (Yeah) / I'm out here on the road / You can hear it in the voice (Glory) / Still get this shit off, though
data.text:
As of this track’s release, there are currently six tracks which are part of the “AM/PM” series:

“9AM in Dallas” (June 2010)

“5AM in Toronto” (March 2013)

“6PM in New York” (February 2015)

“4PM in Calabasas” (June 2016)

“7AM on Bridle Path” (September 2021)
